The '''Grand Alderaanian Gathering''' was an annual social event held on [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] at the [[Okonomo Retreat|Royal Pavilion]]. Not only Alderaanians were invited, but a large number of socialites and military officers, such as then-[[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]], as well. Important Alderaanians such as [[Viceroy/Legends|Viceroy]] [[Bail Prestor Organa/Legends|Bail Organa]] and his daughter [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] also attended.

